Query
------
Search Document by Pol# (GET)                   http://localhost:9090/pc/search/document/NVPA0010010020
Return All Documents                            http://localhost:9090/pc/search/document/all
Return only size & page                         http://localhost:9090/pc/search/document/all?page=1&size=20
Pagination in HTML                              http://localhost:9090/pc/search/document/page/html?page=1&size=40
With JSON View Query                            http://localhost:9090/pc/search/get/all?page=1&size=10
Upload
